01:08:32.073 --> 01:08:33.073
[grunts]

01:08:33.076 --> 01:08:35.710
[yelling]

01:09:09.345 --> 01:09:10.345
Hmm.

01:09:10.346 --> 01:09:12.247
Hey. Hey.

01:09:12.249 --> 01:09:13.715
Got you something.

01:09:13.716 --> 01:09:15.183
I got you something.

01:09:17.685 --> 01:09:19.888
[panting]

01:09:39.375 --> 01:09:41.042
[snorts]

01:09:41.044 --> 01:09:43.478
[gasping]

01:09:43.479 --> 01:09:45.680
Hey. Hey.

01:09:47.816 --> 01:09:49.384
I found something.

01:09:49.386 --> 01:09:51.286
Heh.

01:09:51.287 --> 01:09:52.854
I saw something.

01:09:58.060 --> 01:09:59.160
See?

01:10:00.095 --> 01:10:02.297
Look. They go to the town, probably.

01:10:02.299 --> 01:10:03.298
Oh, my God.

01:10:08.504 --> 01:10:10.705
[music playing]

01:12:06.822 --> 01:12:09.190
[groans]

01:12:09.192 --> 01:12:10.958
Jesus.

01:12:21.170 --> 01:12:23.338
Come on.

01:12:28.143 --> 01:12:29.043
We good?

01:12:29.045 --> 01:12:30.511
Yeah. Let's go.

01:12:33.782 --> 01:12:34.816
After you.

01:12:34.818 --> 01:12:36.384
After you.

01:12:37.753 --> 01:12:39.454
All right. Let's just...

01:12:49.798 --> 01:12:52.100
Is it heavy?

01:12:52.102 --> 01:12:53.534
Yeah.

01:13:01.677 --> 01:13:02.877
Heh.

01:13:02.879 --> 01:13:04.679
[cellphone rings]

01:13:04.681 --> 01:13:06.714
[ring]

01:13:06.716 --> 01:13:09.617
[ring]

01:13:09.619 --> 01:13:11.419
[ring]

01:13:11.421 --> 01:13:12.420
[ring]

01:13:12.422 --> 01:13:14.021
- Answer it.
- Hello.

01:13:14.023 --> 01:13:15.990
Hello. Hello!

01:13:15.992 --> 01:13:18.192
[both laughing]

01:13:26.468 --> 01:13:28.469
[laughter fades]

01:13:38.714 --> 01:13:40.915
[faint siren echoing]

01:13:53.629 --> 01:13:55.630
[music playing]

01:14:35.804 --> 01:14:36.904
[Sunshine barks]

01:14:36.906 --> 01:14:38.673
Ah, you remember Uncle Carter? Huh?

01:14:38.675 --> 01:14:40.007
CARTER: Hey, doggie.

01:14:40.009 --> 01:14:41.776
Ha ha. Hey, what's up?

01:14:41.778 --> 01:14:43.044
How are you, man?

01:14:43.046 --> 01:14:45.213
Oh, I'm good.

01:14:45.215 --> 01:14:46.414
Remember Uncle Carter?

01:14:46.416 --> 01:14:47.582
Real good.

01:14:47.584 --> 01:14:49.617
Hey, Cole.

01:14:49.619 --> 01:14:50.785
- Hi.
- Hi.

01:14:50.787 --> 01:14:52.787
Low five.
[laughs]

01:14:52.789 --> 01:14:54.322
This is everything.

01:14:54.324 --> 01:14:55.523
Yeah? That's it, huh?

01:14:55.525 --> 01:14:56.991
Yeah.

01:14:56.993 --> 01:14:59.494
Are you sure about this?

01:14:59.496 --> 01:15:00.895
- Hey, Cole.
- Yes?

01:15:00.897 --> 01:15:03.664
Why don't you show Uncle
Carter his new room, huh?

01:15:03.666 --> 01:15:04.699
- Yes.
- Yes?

01:15:04.701 --> 01:15:05.700
Good boy, Cole.

01:15:05.702 --> 01:15:07.034
All right. Let's do it.

01:15:07.036 --> 01:15:08.035
All right.

01:15:08.037 --> 01:15:10.004
- Thanks.
- You got it.

01:15:13.675 --> 01:15:15.109
So is this it?

01:15:15.111 --> 01:15:16.310
This is it.

01:15:16.312 --> 01:15:17.311
All right.

01:15:25.821 --> 01:15:28.022
[soundtrack music playing]

01:16:12.968 --> 01:16:15.169
[music continues playing]

01:17:10.192 --> 01:17:11.792
All right, buddy, let's go.

01:17:11.794 --> 01:17:13.527
[grunts]

01:17:15.631 --> 01:17:16.631
There you go.

01:17:16.633 --> 01:17:17.698
You ready?

01:17:20.035 --> 01:17:21.869
Are you sure you're okay with this?

01:17:21.871 --> 01:17:23.871
Are you kidding me, man? It's the least I can do.

01:17:23.873 --> 01:17:27.408
Besides, it'll give me a chance
to knock out a big chunk.

01:17:27.410 --> 01:17:28.209
Yeah.

01:17:28.211 --> 01:17:30.378
I'm proud of you, man.

01:17:30.380 --> 01:17:32.647
Well, it's just flowing from me now.

01:17:32.649 --> 01:17:33.547
[laughs]

01:17:33.549 --> 01:17:35.249
How long is it gonna take you guys

01:17:35.251 --> 01:17:36.250
to circumnavigate the world?

01:17:36.252 --> 01:17:37.785
Uh, you know,

01:17:37.787 --> 01:17:40.021
we're gonna stay with the
parents for a couple days,

01:17:40.023 --> 01:17:42.690
and I'm still not entirely sure
we're gonna get through that,

01:17:42.692 --> 01:17:44.725
but if we do, the tickets are open-ended,

01:17:44.727 --> 01:17:47.628
so we'll just pick a continent
and stay until we get bored

01:17:47.630 --> 01:17:49.597
or, you know, run out of money.

01:17:50.732 --> 01:17:52.800
You know, she's... she's not...

01:17:52.802 --> 01:17:54.535
what I thought, you know?

01:17:54.537 --> 01:17:56.303
I mean...

01:17:56.305 --> 01:17:57.605
I never really knew.

01:17:57.607 --> 01:18:00.474
Yeah, well, she said the same thing about you.

01:18:00.476 --> 01:18:02.843
Yeah.

01:18:02.845 --> 01:18:04.578
All right, come here, you.

01:18:05.914 --> 01:18:07.048
- All right, man.
- See you.

01:18:07.050 --> 01:18:08.082
- Be good.
- All right.

01:18:08.084 --> 01:18:09.917
- Be safe.
- All right.

01:18:09.919 --> 01:18:11.719
All right.

01:18:24.032 --> 01:18:26.233
[gasping]

01:18:59.167 --> 01:19:01.736
[line rings]

01:19:01.738 --> 01:19:03.370
[ring]

01:19:03.372 --> 01:19:04.705
CARTER: Hello.

01:19:04.707 --> 01:19:06.107
Hey.

01:19:06.109 --> 01:19:07.641
I wake you?

01:19:07.643 --> 01:19:10.144
No, I just... I'm finishing some stuff up.

01:19:10.146 --> 01:19:11.812
What's going on?

01:19:11.814 --> 01:19:14.448
Eh, you know,

01:19:14.450 --> 01:19:16.917
I just wanted someone to talk to.

01:19:16.919 --> 01:19:18.986
I'm feeling...

01:19:18.988 --> 01:19:20.488
weird.

01:19:20.490 --> 01:19:23.824
Has it occurred to you that
maybe you need some sleep?

01:19:23.826 --> 01:19:25.426
[sighs] I guess...

01:19:25.428 --> 01:19:27.862
I thought that I was past the point

01:19:27.864 --> 01:19:31.031
where I really believed that people could change,
you know?

01:19:31.033 --> 01:19:34.368
At least, the point where I thought that I could.

01:19:34.370 --> 01:19:36.804
Sounds like a pleasant surprise, no?

01:19:36.806 --> 01:19:38.305
Yeah. Absolutely,

01:19:38.307 --> 01:19:41.041
but I'm just not sure I believe it.

01:19:41.043 --> 01:19:42.443
Believe what?

01:19:42.445 --> 01:19:44.478
That I'm really doing this.

01:19:44.480 --> 01:19:47.581
Well, what exactly is the alternative?

01:19:47.583 --> 01:19:49.550
Well, this is gonna sound a little crazy.

01:19:49.552 --> 01:19:52.286
Imagine that.
You called me in the middle of the night

01:19:52.288 --> 01:19:53.988
with something that sounds a little crazy?

01:19:53.990 --> 01:19:55.890
Part of me believes that...

01:19:57.526 --> 01:20:00.361
we never made it out of that desert...

01:20:01.797 --> 01:20:04.832
that we're just lying there, overcome...

01:20:06.468 --> 01:20:09.703
and this is just all part of our imagination.

01:20:09.705 --> 01:20:12.706
I told you this was gonna sound crazy, but...

01:20:12.708 --> 01:20:15.609
And you didn't sell it short.

01:20:15.611 --> 01:20:18.879
A... Are you telling me that
you're not at all suspicious

01:20:18.881 --> 01:20:21.482
that things have gone so smoothly?

01:20:21.484 --> 01:20:23.117
Suspicious? No.

01:20:23.119 --> 01:20:25.419
I'm stunned, I'm impressed,

01:20:25.421 --> 01:20:27.388
but I'm not suspicious.

01:20:27.390 --> 01:20:29.423
Well, maybe you should be.

01:20:29.425 --> 01:20:30.825
I mean, think about it.

01:20:30.827 --> 01:20:33.527
Things may be just a little too good to be true,

01:20:33.529 --> 01:20:34.728
you know what I mean?

01:20:34.730 --> 01:20:36.964
Believe me, if I was making this up,

01:20:36.966 --> 01:20:39.700
there'd be a lot more lottery
winning and supermodeling.

01:20:39.702 --> 01:20:42.436
Well, at least convince me that it's probable,

01:20:42.438 --> 01:20:43.804
you know, that life really

01:20:43.806 --> 01:20:46.440
can turn on a dime, that you really can...

01:20:46.442 --> 01:20:47.741
I don't know... reinvent yourself.

01:20:47.743 --> 01:20:49.410
Which is harder to believe,

01:20:49.412 --> 01:20:52.680
that things are finally going the
way you always wanted them to

01:20:52.682 --> 01:20:54.715
or that the only way it could be this good

01:20:54.717 --> 01:20:56.283
is if it's all in your head?

01:20:56.285 --> 01:20:57.451
I don't know.

01:20:57.453 --> 01:20:59.119
You don't have an opinion on that?

01:20:59.121 --> 01:21:00.688
Well, I don't know about you,

01:21:00.690 --> 01:21:02.289
but this better be reality for me,

01:21:02.291 --> 01:21:04.158
because if we're still out in the middle

01:21:04.160 --> 01:21:05.426
of the desert somewhere,

01:21:05.428 --> 01:21:07.494
I just finished an imaginary book.

01:21:07.496 --> 01:21:11.298
Wow, that's... That's really, really fast.

01:21:11.300 --> 01:21:13.767
So tell me how it ends.

01:21:13.769 --> 01:21:16.070
Well, that's the funny thi...

01:21:16.072 --> 01:21:18.239
[static clicks]

01:21:18.241 --> 01:21:19.974
Carter?

01:21:21.176 --> 01:21:22.509
Carter?

01:21:27.148 --> 01:21:28.616
Piece of shit.

01:21:28.618 --> 01:21:30.117
[cellphone clatters]

01:21:30.119 --> 01:21:31.418
[rings]

01:21:33.688 --> 01:21:35.689
[ring]

01:21:37.092 --> 01:21:38.792
[ring]

01:21:40.428 --> 01:21:41.629
[ring]

01:21:43.265 --> 01:21:45.566
[ring]

01:21:47.335 --> 01:21:48.903
